|9 |              └─SORT                              |           |1       |46          |
|10|                └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN                |           |1       |46          |
|11|                  ├─NESTED-LOOP JOIN              |           |1       |29          |
|12|                  │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN             |item       |1       |13          |
|13|                  │ └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE RANGE SCAN|store_sales|2       |16          |
|14|                  └─DISTRIBUTED TABLE GET         |date_dim   |1       |16          |
